SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 71-5-1503(a)(4), is amended by
deleting the language "thirty (30) business days" and substituting "forty-five (45) calendar days".
SECTION 2. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 71-5-1506, is amended by adding
the following new subsection:
(c) Notwithstanding ยง 68-140-319, the office of emergency services shall provide
the commissioner of health with full access to ambulance run reports maintained by the
office. The commissioner of health may provide the bureau with ambulance run report
data and additional requested data, including reports containing protected health
information, as needed to ensure the assessment program remains in compliance with
state and federal laws.
SECTION 3. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 71-5-1509, is amended by deleting
the language "June 30, 2025" and substituting "June 30, 2026".
SECTION 4. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
